        "| `signal_type` | A label for the type of signal being scored (e.g., `\"RISK_SIGNAL\"` or `\"TARGET_SIGNAL\"`) |\n",
        "| `**score` | The dictionary returned by `score_chunk_for_signal()` (e.g., booleans, counts, confidence scores) |\n"
